{{Infobox film festival | name = Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival | logo = File:Sarajevo.fashion.film.festival.jpg | logo_caption = Official logo | image = | image_size = 250px | caption = | founded = {{start date and age|2015}} | number = | location = [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | language = International | website = {{URL|http://www.sfff.ba/}} }} The '''Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival''' ({{lang-bs|Sarajevski festival modnog filma / Сарајевски фестивал модног филма}}) is an international [[film festival]] held annually in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sarajevotimes.com/creator-amela-radan-bring-sophia-loren-sarajevo/|title=Our Fashion Creator Amela Radan to bring Sophia Loren to Sarajevo|publisher=Sarajevo Times}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfff.ba/about.php|title=About|publisher=official website}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.modamo.info/index.php/moda/novosti/15382-sutra-u-sarajevu-pocinje-sarajevo-fashion-film-festival|title=Sutra u Sarajevu počinje Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=modamo.info}}</ref> It exclusively showcases fashion films, advertising films, music videos and short documentaries on the fashion industry. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://filmfreeway.com/SarajevoFFF|title=Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=filmfreeway.com}}</ref> It was established in 2015 by the Consortio Civium Invictum Foundation in cooperation with the [[London Fashion Week]], [[Paris Fashion Week]] and the [[Madrid Fashion Film Festival]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://faktor.ba/vijest/nasa-kreatorica-putuje-u-hollywood-amela-radan-u-sarajevo-dovodi-sophiju-loren-265769|title=Naša kreatorica putuje u Hollywood: Amela Radan u Sarajevo dovodi Sophiju Loren|publisher=faktor.ba}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ekskluziva.ba/u-hotelu-hills-otvoren-drugi-medunarodni-sarajevo-fashion-film-festival-galerija/261535|title=U Hotelu Hills otvoren drugi međunarodni Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=ekskluziva.ba}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.christosmarkou.co.uk/blog/2017/12/2/orange-wonder-sarajevo-fashion-film-festival|title="Orange Wonder" @Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=christosmarkou.co.uk}}</ref>
==Format== SFFF was created in order to showcase and exhibit the new fashion cinematographic genre to wider audiences as well to create an institutional background to the increasing number of fashion films produced every year by fashion magazines and fashion production companies. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://style.rs/tagovi/sarajevo-fashion-film-festival/|title=Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=style.rs}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://serbiafashionweek.com/en/2017/12/05/sfw-recognition-sfff/|title=Recognition for international impact on the fashion industry at the SFFF|publisher=serbiafashionweek.com}}</ref> The festival is held in December of every year and lasts for two days. It is made up of a competition and non-competition programme. As of 2017, the former is divided into 14 categories and includes the Dove of Sarajevo award for best overall fashion film. Further categories include Best Fashion Film, Best Music Video, Best National Film, Best New Talent, Best Photography, Best Actor, Best Actress, Best Cinematography, Best Costume Design, Best Major Brand Production, Best Make-up and Hair, Best Story, Best Visual and Special Effect and Best Documentary. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joshbrandao.com/about-contact|title=Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival editorials|publisher=joshbrandao.com}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joakimlund.com/2017/11/16/official-selection-sarajevo-fashion-film-festival/|title=Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival official selection|publisher=joakimlund.com}}</ref> The maximum length of the films shown in the competitive selection is 20 minutes. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.modamo.info/index.php/moda/novosti/15382-sutra-u-sarajevu-pocinje-sarajevo-fashion-film-festival|title=Počinje Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival|publisher=modamo.info}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hadimoussally.com/the12projectteaser.html|title=Sarajevo Fashion Film Festival selection|publisher=hadimoussally.com}}</ref> ==Award winners== ''Selected categ